column9: Sponsor Bank - Christine Hermanson Grant Program

column4: A sponsor code is created automatically when a membership is created.  (Member number + "A")
The sponsor code is not available for use until the member becomes an Ensemble Member.
New Ensemble Member will have sponsor code appear on their Member Dashboard.
Member provides sponsor code to a school who uses the code upon entering subscription.
Ensemble Member Dashboard will show name of entity being sponsored.
If the Ensemble Member does not use the sponsor code within a certain period of time, it goes into the bank
Use of a promotion code overrides the subscription criteria and replaces it with any value in the
corresponding column of the promotion code table.  Each code is active from the start date until
